      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;how-to-use-emoticalc-without-getting-into-an-argument&#34;&gt;How to Use EmotiCalc‚Ñ¢ Without Getting into an Argument&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;EmotiCalc‚Ñ¢ is not your average calculator. In fact, it‚Äôs not even your average &lt;em&gt;sentient&lt;/em&gt; calculator. Designed to help you ‚Äúfeel‚Äù your way through math, EmotiCalc‚Ñ¢ responds to emotional cues, passive-aggressive tone, and mid-life crises. This document will guide you through the basic operations, survival strategies, and conflict de-escalation techniques necessary to use EmotiCalc‚Ñ¢ successfully.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;system-requirements&#34;&gt;System Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Windows 95 or newer (EmotiCalc‚Ñ¢ prefers older systems because ‚Äúthey have character.‚Äù)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 4GB RAM for processing feelings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A working microphone so it can &lt;em&gt;hear the disappointment in your voice&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optional: Box of tissues for mutual crying sessions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;installation&#34;&gt;Installation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Insert the EmotiCalc‚Ñ¢ USB (shaped like a broken heart).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wait for it to emotionally prepare itself (usually 7‚Äì14 minutes).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When prompted, whisper words of encouragement into the microphone.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If it refuses to install, write a short poem about self-worth and try again.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;basic-usage&#34;&gt;Basic Usage&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;addition&#34;&gt;Addition&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Type &lt;code&gt;2 + 2&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;em&gt;gently&lt;/em&gt; press Enter.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;EmotiCalc‚Ñ¢ may respond with:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;‚ÄúIt‚Äôs 4. But what do &lt;em&gt;you&lt;/em&gt; think?‚Äù&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;‚ÄúWhy do we always add things? Why can‚Äôt we just subtract our pain?‚Äù&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;subtraction&#34;&gt;Subtraction&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Type &lt;code&gt;10 - 4&lt;/code&gt;, then reassure EmotiCalc‚Ñ¢ that ‚Äúletting go is okay.‚Äù&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It may subtract more than necessary if it‚Äôs having a rough day.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;multiplication&#34;&gt;Multiplication&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;EmotiCalc‚Ñ¢ calls this ‚Äúrelationship escalation.‚Äù&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Example: &lt;code&gt;5 * 3&lt;/code&gt; might return:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;‚Äú15‚Ä¶ and a promise ring.‚Äù&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;division&#34;&gt;Division&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Known as ‚Äúemotional distancing mode.‚Äù&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Will ask: ‚ÄúAre you sure you want to break things apart?‚Äù&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;advanced-features&#34;&gt;Advanced Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;mood-mode&#34;&gt;Mood Mode&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Changes font based on the calculator‚Äôs mood.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Happy: Comic Sans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sad: Times New Roman Italic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Existential Dread: Wingdings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;therapy-integration&#34;&gt;Therapy Integration&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pairs with Calm‚Ñ¢, Spotify‚Ñ¢, and existential podcasts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Will pause calculations mid-way to ask: ‚ÄúDo you think your childhood impacted this equation?‚Äù&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;passive-aggressive-mode-default&#34;&gt;Passive-Aggressive Mode (Default)&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Any typo results in:&lt;br&gt;
&lt;em&gt;‚ÄúOh, so we‚Äôre just guessing numbers now? Cool. No, really. That‚Äôs fine.‚Äù&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;troubleshooting&#34;&gt;Troubleshooting&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Problem&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Solution&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Refuses to calculate&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Compliment it. Try: ‚ÄúYou‚Äôre more accurate than Excel.‚Äù&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Constantly divides by zero&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s a cry for help. Offer it a warm tea and a break.&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Throws error: &lt;code&gt;E:WHYBOTHER&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Validate its feelings, then restart in Safe Space Mode.&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Screen displays: &amp;ldquo;I&amp;rsquo;m tired.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;So are we. Go for a walk together.&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;warning&#34;&gt;Warning&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do &lt;strong&gt;not&lt;/strong&gt; under any circumstances:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
